						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Rājēndra I, Year 29 = 1041 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the building of the shrines of Kshētrapāla and Chaṇḍēśvara by Mummuḍichōḻanāti, son of Vayiśraṇabaktoṉparam and a subordinate of Uttamachōḻa-puṟamalai-nāḍāḻvāṉ. [This inscription is engraved below the above inscription and therefore this could belong to 29th, Year].</p>						

